race.comment: CROSS TASMAN (7) undefeated in three runs this prep and keeps spacing his rivals by big margins. Ploughed through the heavy (8) conditions with dominant win over 1500m at this track last time out. Berry hops back on and expected to justify the short price. AMPLIFY (10) resumed after finishing unplaced in the Queensland Oaks with a fast finishing victory over 1400m at Randwick in good style. Kept fresh for this with a 1200m trial placing at Warwick Farm. Serious contender on the limit and should get enough tempo to surge late. Main danger. IPPIE BEACH (8) meets CROSS TASMAN slightly better at the weights with J Mac aboard. Got her desired conditions last start with a battling third in the heavy conditions. Look for her running on. JUST PARTY (3) deep into the prep and keep safe.
